<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2026-02-07T12:41:32+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, 20 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">Joshua Breakstone</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260207/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Joshua Breakstone" /><published>2026-02-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/joshua-breakstone</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260207/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Jazz guitarist Joshua Breakstone performing at <a href="https://bondsrosary.com" target="_blank">Bond's Rosary</a> in Gion. 
</p>
<p class="en">
I had to move as far back as I could to fit him into the view of my 50mm lens, but I liked what of all the out of focus elements on my table added to the picture.

</p>
<p class="jp">
ジャズ・ギタリスト、ジョシュア・ブレークストーンが祇園の<a href="https://bondsrosary.com" target="_blank">ボンズ・ロザリー</a>で演奏している。
</p>
<p class="jp">
50mmレンズの視界に彼を収めるため、かなり後ろに下がる必要があったが、テーブル上のボケた物たちが写真に良いアクセントになった。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Concerts" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Jazz guitarist Joshua Breakstone performing at Bond's Rosary in Gion. I had to move as far back as I could to fit him into the view of my 50mm lens, but I liked what of all the out of focus elements on my table added to the picture.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03329_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03329_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">River Pine・川の松</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260206/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="River Pine・川の松" /><published>2026-02-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/river-pine</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260206/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A pine tree along the Oi River, bathed in morning light. 
</p>
<p class="jp">
大堰川の岸辺の松が朝の光を浴びている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A pine tree along the Oi River, bathed in morning light. 大堰川の岸辺の松が朝の光を浴びている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03263_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03263_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Umezono・梅園</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260205/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Umezono・梅園" /><published>2026-02-05T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-05T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/umezono</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260205/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Retro Showa Era elegance of this sweets shop in the Teramachi shopping arcade.
</p>
<p class="jp">
寺町商店街に佇む老舗甘味処・梅園の風情ある佇まい。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Retro Showa Era elegance of this sweets shop in the Teramachi shopping arcade. 寺町商店街に佇む老舗甘味処・梅園の風情ある佇まい。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03222.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03222.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260204/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社" /><published>2026-02-04T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-04T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kurumazaki-jinja</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260204/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Looking thru the Shimmon Gate at Kurmazaki Jinja shrine, as daylight fades.
</p>
<p class="jp">
日が暮れゆく中、車折神社の神門越しに眺める。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Shrines" /><category term="Dusk" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking thru the Shimmon Gate at Kurmazaki Jinja shrine, as daylight fades. 日が暮れゆく中、車折神社の神門越しに眺める。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03252_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03252_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Setsubun・節分</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260203/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Setsubun・節分" /><published>2026-02-03T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-03T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/setsubun</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260203/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maiko" target="_blank">maiko</a> throws bags of soybeans into the crowd, used to drive away evil spirits on <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Setsubun" target="_blank">Setsubun</a>, a traditional holiday celebrating the end of winter. Taken at Kitano Tenmangu Shrine.
</p>
<p class="jp">
節分で、<a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/舞妓" target="_blank">舞妓</a>が邪気を払うための大豆の袋を群衆に投げ入れる。<a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/節分" target="_blank">節分</a>は冬の終わりを祝う伝統的な行事である。北野天満宮にて撮影。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A maiko throws bags of soybeans into the crowd, used to drive away evil spirits on Setsubun, a traditional holiday celebrating the end of winter. Taken at Kitano Tenmangu Shrine. 節分で、舞妓が邪気を払うための大豆の袋を群衆に投げ入れる。節分は冬の終わりを祝う伝統的な行事である。北野天満宮にて撮影。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03203.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03203.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260201/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋" /><published>2026-02-01T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-01T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/togetssukyo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260201/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A couple enjoys the view from Arashiyama's Togetsukyo bridge. The pagoda of Horin-ji temple is in the background.
</p>
<p class="jp">
嵐山の渡月橋からの眺めを楽しむカップル。法輪寺の塔が背景に見える。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A couple enjoys the view from Arashiyama's Togetsukyo bridge. The pagoda of Horin-ji temple is in the background. 嵐山の渡月橋からの眺めを楽しむカップル。法輪寺の塔が背景に見える。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R02958_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R02958_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Red, White, &amp;amp; Green・赤白緑</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260131/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Red, White, &amp;amp; Green・赤白緑" /><published>2026-01-31T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-31T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/palestine</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260131/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Palestinian flags at a demonstration in front of Kyoto's City Hall.
</p>
