京都市役所前の抗議デモでのパレスチナ国旗。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Street" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Palestinian flags at a demonstration in front of Kyoto's City Hall. 京都市役所前の抗議デモでのパレスチナ国旗。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2354_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_DSC_2354_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260130/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Togetsu Bridge・渡月橋" /><published>2026-01-30T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-30T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/togetsu</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260130/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
