</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking east at dusk, over the Katsura River and Togetsukyo bridge. 夕暮れ時、桂川と渡月橋越しに東を見る。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_IMG_3203_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_IMG_3203_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Umeda・梅田</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260124/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Umeda・梅田" /><published>2026-01-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/umeda</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260124/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Catching the last glimmer of sunlight in this long exposure on Yotsubashi-Suji street.
</p>
<p class="jp">
四ツ橋筋、長時間露光で夕暮れの残光を写す。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Osaka" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Architecture" /><category term="Street" /><category term="Long Exposure" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Catching the last glimmer of sunlight in this long exposure on Yotsubashi-Suji street. 四ツ橋筋、長時間露光で夕暮れの残光を写す。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_A7R02815_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2601_A7R02815_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Takano River・高野川</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260123/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Takano River・高野川" /><published>2026-01-23T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-01-23T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/takanogawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260123/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
